					<p>
						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/obama/" rel="category tag">Obama</a></span>
						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/elections/" rel="tag">elections</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/iran/" rel="tag">Iran</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/medvedev/" rel="tag">Medvedev</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/obama/" rel="tag">Obama</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/russia/" rel="tag">russia</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/usa/" rel="tag">USA</a></span>					</p>
