						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/arms/" rel="tag">arms</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/overwhelming-demand/" rel="tag">Overwhelming Demand</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/ruger/" rel="tag">Ruger</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/usa/" rel="tag">USA</a></span>					</p>
